- Good.

529
00:26:29,348 --> 00:26:31,320
Hallie, what did he say?
- What didn't he say?

530
00:26:31,582 --> 00:26:33,338
I can't tell you how sorry I am.

531
00:26:33,668 --> 00:26:35,552
