549
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:15,763
Our marriage.
- Marriage?

550
00:27:16,127 --> 00:27:17,400
Are you proposing marriage?

551
00:27:17,985 --> 00:27:20,327
Don't pretend you didn't know.
You knew that I loved you.

552
00:27:20,682 --> 00:27:22,365
How do you know who or what I am?

553
00:27:22,922 --> 00:27:24,643
I don't care who or what you are.

554
00:27:24,855 --> 00:27:26,499
A woman's life begins with her <i>tomorrow</i>.

555
00:27:26,776 --> 00:27:27,934
Not with her <i>yesterday</i>.

556
00:27:28,290 --> 00:27:31,040
