- A woman's tomorrow?

557
00:27:31,519 --> 00:27:32,752
Where did you read that?

558
00:27:34,099 --> 00:27:35,052
Don't make fun.

559
00:27:35,495 --> 00:27:36,798
Don't be too serious.

560
00:27:37,326 --> 00:27:39,351
