- I'll call you.

578
00:28:23,802 --> 00:28:25,333
I'll wait for your call.
- Alright.

579
00:28:27,755 --> 00:28:29,199
I'll be in my room.
- Okay.

580
00:28:31,610 --> 00:28:33,833
