00:31:39,235 --> 00:31:43,097
And David's put her in Mrs Stone's room.
- Alright, I'm coming right up.

638
00:31:43,294 --> 00:31:44,575
It's sacrilege, I say.

639
00:31:44,892 --> 00:31:47,068
I told them not to take ..
- Alright. I'm coming.

640
00:31:47,533 --> 00:31:48,262
Alright.

641
00:31:50,116 --> 00:31:51,017
That marriage.

642
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:53,441
Must have been quite a
shock to you, Mr Stone.

643
00:31:53,734 --> 00:31:55,025
Yes. It was.

644
00:31:56,129 --> 00:31:58,129
Yes, she certainly
took that kid of yours.

645
00:31:58,550 --> 00:32:00,862
But she's bad news if
I know it when I see it.

646
00:32:01,059 --> 00:32:01,703
Oh?

647
00:32:02,321 --> 00:32:04,305
Yeah. The kid is daffy about her.

648
00:32:05,249 --> 00:32:07,666
But she's a cold dish if ever I saw one.

649
00:32:08,577 --> 00:32:09,850
Can I give you a lift, sir?

650
00:32:10,082 --> 00:32:11,544
No thank you. No, I'll walk.

651
00:32:12,002 --> 00:32:13,577
I'll walk along with you, Mr Stone.

652
00:32:13,950 --> 00:32:15,794
You don't mind if I leave
my car here, do you?

653
00:32:15,991 --> 00:32:16,892
Certainly not.

654
00:32:17,456 --> 00:32:18,250
Thank you.

655
00:32:20,989 --> 00:32:22,305
Hello there, Mr Stone.

656
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:24,228
Hello there, Mrs Stone.

657
00:32:24,425 --> 00:32:26,041
I didn't know you had a home like this.

658
00:32:26,275 --> 00:32:27,581
Do you like it?
- Hmm.

659
00:32:28,326 --> 00:32:29,645
Father built it for mother.

660
00:32:29,964 --> 00:32:31,482
Yes? Must have cost plenty.

661
00:32:32,223 --> 00:32:34,742
Plenty? Father doesn't
care what he spends.

662
00:32:35,088 --> 00:32:36,803
As long as it's for
something worthwhile.

663
00:32:37,348 --> 00:32:38,879
The church out there.
- Worthwhile?

664
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,848
What do you mean?
- Well.

665
00:32:41,627 --> 00:32:43,030
His home and his church.

666
00:32:43,491 --> 00:32:44,278
His books.

667
00:32:44,657 --> 00:32:45,970
That's father.
- Really?

668
00:32:46,594 --> 00:32:47,523
He sounds nice.

669
00:32:48,170 --> 00:32:49,745
He is. Just wait until you meet him.

670
00:32:57,679 --> 00:32:58,522
That's Mark.

671
00:32:59,457 --> 00:33:01,284
Let's go upstairs.
I want to powder my nose.

672
00:33:01,867 --> 00:33:02,596
Alright.

673
00:33:16,739 --> 00:33:19,128
When young folks fall
in love, there is ..

674
00:33:19,518 --> 00:33:21,365
