675
00:33:27,237 --> 00:33:29,556
Hmm. Maybe it's nice after all.

676
00:33:30,849 --> 00:33:31,523
Nice?

677
00:33:33,022 --> 00:33:35,057
Ask anyone around that hotel about her.

678
00:33:35,488 --> 00:33:36,475
They'll tell you.

679
